abstract: The bank’s profit, which still beat expectations, was squeezed by a combination of rising expenses and low interest rates.
snippet: The bank’s profit, which still beat expectations, was squeezed by a combination of rising expenses and low interest rates.
lead_paragraph: Wells Fargo’s profit machine showed signs of slowing in the first quarter as the bank reported a rare decline in net income from a year ago.

headline.main: Wells Fargo Posts Rare Decline in Quarterly Net Income
